{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":578,"text":"I'm a brain scientist, and as a brain scientist,"},{"time":3675,"text":"I'm actually interested in how the brain learns,"},{"time":6747,"text":"and I'm especially interested in a possibility of"},{"time":10114,"text":"making our brains smarter, better and faster."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14846,"text":"This is in this context I'm going to tell you"},{"time":17722,"text":"about video games. When we say video games,"},{"time":20472,"text":"most of you think about children."},{"time":23010,"text":"It's true. Ninety percent of children do play video games."},{"time":26988,"text":"But let's be frank."},{"time":29906,"text":"When the kids are in bed, who is in front of the PlayStation?"},{"time":34695,"text":"Most of you. The average age of a gamer is 33 years old,"},{"time":41179,"text":"not eight years old, and in fact, if we look"},{"time":44186,"text":"at the projected demographics of video game play,"},{"time":47895,"text":"the video game players of tomorrow are"},{"time":50628,"text":"older adults. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":53752,"text":"So video [gaming] is pervasive throughout our society."},{"time":58003,"text":"It is clearly here to stay. It has an amazing impact"},{"time":62386,"text":"on our everyday life. Consider these statistics"},{"time":65773,"text":"released by Activision. After one month of release"},{"time":71588,"text":"of the game \"Call Of Duty: Black Ops,\" it had been played"},{"time":76080,"text":"for 68,000 years"},{"time":79453,"text":"worldwide, right?"},{"time":81319,"text":"Would any of you complain if this was the case"},{"time":84266,"text":"about doing linear algebra?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":87429,"text":"So what we are asking in the lab is, how can we leverage that power?"},{"time":91724,"text":"Now I want to step back a bit."},{"time":93572,"text":"I know most of you have had the experience of coming back"},{"time":96813,"text":"home and finding your kids playing these kinds of games."},{"time":101533,"text":"(Shooting noises) The name of the game is to get"},{"time":103673,"text":"after your enemy zombie bad guys"},{"time":106637,"text":"before they get to you, right?"},{"time":110227,"text":"And I'm almost sure most of you have thought,"},{"time":113404,"text":"\"Oh, come on, can't you do something more intelligent"},{"time":116725,"text":"than shooting at zombies?\""},{"time":120052,"text":"I'd like you to put this kind of knee-jerk reaction"},{"time":123518,"text":"in the context of what you would have thought"},{"time":126015,"text":"if you had found your girl playing sudoku"},{"time":129524,"text":"or your boy reading Shakespeare. Right?"},{"time":133875,"text":"Most parents would find that great."},{"time":136612,"text":"Well, I'm not going to tell you that playing video games"},{"time":139956,"text":"days in and days out is actually good for your health."},{"time":142924,"text":"It's not, and binging is never good."},{"time":146124,"text":"But I'm going to argue that in reasonable doses,"},{"time":150115,"text":"actually the very game I showed you at the beginning,"},{"time":153084,"text":"those action-packed shooter games"},{"time":155668,"text":"have quite powerful effects and positive effects"},{"time":159444,"text":"on many different aspects of our behavior."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163302,"text":"There's not one week that goes without some major"},{"time":166997,"text":"headlines in the media about whether video games are"},{"time":169773,"text":"good or bad for you, right? You're all bombarded with that."},{"time":174389,"text":"I'd like to put this kind of Friday night bar discussion aside"},{"time":180077,"text":"and get you to actually step into the lab."},{"time":183220,"text":"What we do in the lab is actually measure directly,"},{"time":186093,"text":"in a quantitative fashion, what is the impact"},{"time":188860,"text":"of video games on the brain."},{"time":191629,"text":"And so I'm going to take a few examples from our work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194964,"text":"One first saying that I'm sure you all have heard"},{"time":197563,"text":"is the fact that too much screen time"},{"time":199849,"text":"makes your eyesight worse."},{"time":202664,"text":"That's a statement about vision."},{"time":204867,"text":"There may be vision scientists among you."},{"time":207403,"text":"We actually know how to test that statement."},{"time":210342,"text":"We can step into the lab and measure how good your vision is."},{"time":213779,"text":"Well, guess what? People that don't play a lot"},{"time":217460,"text":"of action games, that don't actually spend a lot of time"},{"time":220450,"text":"in front of screens, have normal, or what we call"},{"time":223982,"text":"corrective-to-normal vision. That's okay."},{"time":226636,"text":"The issue is what happens with these guys that actually"},{"time":229085,"text":"indulge into playing video games like five hours per week,"},{"time":232365,"text":"10 hours per week, 15 hours per week."},{"time":234240,"text":"By that statement, their vision should be really bad, right?"},{"time":237468,"text":"Guess what? Their vision is really, really good."},{"time":240165,"text":"It's better than those that don't play."},{"time":242605,"text":"And it's better in two different ways."},{"time":244877,"text":"The first way is that they're actually able to resolve"},{"time":247302,"text":"small detail in the context of clutter, and though that means"},{"time":250557,"text":"being able to read the fine print on a prescription"},{"time":254355,"text":"rather than using magnifier glasses, you can actually do it"},{"time":258982,"text":"with just your eyesight."},{"time":260548,"text":"The other way that they are better is actually being able"},{"time":263364,"text":"to resolve different levels of gray."},{"time":266273,"text":"Imagine you're driving in a fog. That makes a difference"},{"time":269444,"text":"between seeing the car in front of you"},{"time":271925,"text":"and avoiding the accident, or getting into an accident."},{"time":275668,"text":"So we're actually leveraging that work to develop games"},{"time":278684,"text":"for patients with low vision, and to have an impact"},{"time":283158,"text":"on retraining their brain to see better."},{"time":286493,"text":"Clearly, when it comes to action video games,"},{"time":290142,"text":"screen time doesn't make your eyesight worse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":293037,"text":"Another saying that I'm sure you have all heard around:"},{"time":297023,"text":"Video games lead to attention problems and greater distractability."},{"time":301397,"text":"Okay, we know how to measure attention in the lab."},{"time":305302,"text":"I'm actually going to give you an example of how we do so."},{"time":308903,"text":"I'm going to ask you to participate, so you're going to have"},{"time":311628,"text":"to actually play the game with me. I'm going to show you"},{"time":314652,"text":"colored words. I want you to shout out the color of the ink."},{"time":320085,"text":"Right? So this is the first example."},{"time":323468,"text":"[\"Chair\"]"},{"time":324558,"text":"Orange, good. [\"Table\"] Green."},{"time":327619,"text":"[\"Board\"] Audience: Red.Daphne Bavelier: Red."},{"time":328999,"text":"[\"Horse\"] DB: Yellow. Audience: Yellow."},{"time":330293,"text":"[\"Yellow\"] DB: Red. Audience: Yellow."},{"time":331618,"text":"[\"Blue\"] DB: Yellow."},{"time":333127,"text":"Okay, you get my point, right? (Laughter)"},{"time":339482,"text":"You're getting better, but it's hard. Why is it hard?"},{"time":342818,"text":"Because I introduced a conflict between"},{"time":346772,"text":"the word itself and its color."},{"time":349685,"text":"How good your attention is determines actually how fast"},{"time":352724,"text":"you resolve that conflict, so the young guys here"},{"time":355251,"text":"at the top of their game probably, like, did a little better"},{"time":357812,"text":"than some of us that are older."},{"time":360356,"text":"What we can show is that when you do this kind of task"},{"time":362924,"text":"with people that play a lot of action games,"},{"time":364524,"text":"they actually resolve the conflict faster."},{"time":367844,"text":"So clearly playing those action games doesn't lead"},{"time":371052,"text":"to attention problems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373535,"text":"Actually, those action video game players have"},{"time":375506,"text":"many other advantages in terms of attention, and one"},{"time":377823,"text":"aspect of attention which is also improved for the better"},{"time":380722,"text":"is our ability to track objects around in the world."},{"time":385500,"text":"This is something we use all the time. When you're driving,"},{"time":388044,"text":"you're tracking, keeping track of the cars around you."},{"time":391292,"text":"You're also keeping track of the pedestrian, the running dog,"},{"time":394367,"text":"and that's how you can actually be safe driving, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":397420,"text":"In the lab, we get people to come to the lab,"},{"time":400484,"text":"sit in front of a computer screen, and we give them"},{"time":402564,"text":"little tasks that I'm going to get you to do again."},{"time":405460,"text":"You're going to see yellow happy faces"},{"time":408412,"text":"and a few sad blue faces. These are children"},{"time":412228,"text":"in the schoolyard in Geneva during a recess"},{"time":416048,"text":"during the winter. Most kids are happy. It's actually recess."},{"time":420349,"text":"But a few kids are sad and blue because they've forgotten their coat."},{"time":423476,"text":"Everybody begins to move around, and your task"},{"time":426796,"text":"is to keep track of who had a coat at the beginning"},{"time":429920,"text":"and who didn't. So I'm just going to show you an example"},{"time":432411,"text":"where there is only one sad kid. It's easy because you can"},{"time":435240,"text":"actually track it with your eyes. You can track,"},{"time":437577,"text":"you can track, and then when it stops, and there is"},{"time":439857,"text":"a question mark, and I ask you, did this kid have a coat or not?"},{"time":443788,"text":"Was it yellow initially or blue?"},{"time":446616,"text":"I hear a few yellow. Good. So most of you have a brain. (Laughter)"},{"time":450413,"text":"I'm now going to ask you to do the task, but now with"},{"time":455209,"text":"a little more challenging task. There are going to be"},{"time":457297,"text":"three of them that are blue. Don't move your eyes."},{"time":460480,"text":"Please don't move your eyes. Keep your eyes fixated"},{"time":462733,"text":"and expand, pull your attention. That's the only way"},{"time":465379,"text":"you can actually do it. If you move your eyes, you're doomed."},{"time":468227,"text":"Yellow or blue?"},{"time":469690,"text":"Audience: Yellow.DB: Good."},{"time":471336,"text":"So your typical normal young adult"},{"time":473839,"text":"can have a span of about three or four objects of attention."},{"time":477475,"text":"That's what we just did. Your action video game player"},{"time":480235,"text":"has a span of about six to seven objects of attention,"},{"time":483435,"text":"which is what is shown in this video here."},{"time":486413,"text":"That's for you guys, action video game players."},{"time":489889,"text":"A bit more challenging, right? (Laughter)"},{"time":491774,"text":"Yellow or blue? Blue. We have some people"},{"time":495482,"text":"that are serious out there. Yeah. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":498686,"text":"Good. So in the same way that we actually see"},{"time":502290,"text":"the effects of video games on people's behavior,"},{"time":505768,"text":"we can use brain imaging and look at the impact"},{"time":508833,"text":"of video games on the brain, and we do find many changes,"},{"time":512618,"text":"but the main changes are actually to the brain networks"},{"time":515978,"text":"that control attention. So one part is the parietal cortex"},{"time":520522,"text":"which is very well known to control the orientation of attention."},{"time":524241,"text":"The other one is the frontal lobe, which controls"},{"time":526674,"text":"how we sustain attention, and another one"},{"time":529384,"text":"is the anterior cingulate, which controls how we allocate"},{"time":531953,"text":"and regulate attention and resolve conflict."},{"time":535250,"text":"Now, when we do brain imaging, we find that all three"},{"time":538114,"text":"of these networks are actually much more efficient"},{"time":541458,"text":"in people that play action games."}]},{"cues":[{"time":544218,"text":"This actually leads me to a rather counterintuitive finding"},{"time":548969,"text":"in the literature about technology and the brain."},{"time":552410,"text":"You all know about multitasking. You all have been faulty"},{"time":556859,"text":"of multitasking when you're driving"},{"time":559069,"text":"and you pick up your cellphone. Bad idea. Very bad idea."},{"time":563760,"text":"Why? Because as your attention shifts to your cell phone,"},{"time":567663,"text":"you are actually losing the capacity to react swiftly"},{"time":571811,"text":"to the car braking in front of you, and so you're"},{"time":574259,"text":"much more likely to get engaged into a car accident."},{"time":579830,"text":"Now, we can measure that kind of skills in the lab."},{"time":582706,"text":"We obviously don't ask people to drive around and see"},{"time":585178,"text":"how many car accidents they have. That would be a little"},{"time":587523,"text":"costly proposition. But we design tasks on the computer"},{"time":591070,"text":"where we can measure, to millisecond accuracy,"},{"time":594188,"text":"how good they are at switching from one task to another."},{"time":598716,"text":"When we do that, we actually find that people"},{"time":601284,"text":"that play a lot of action games are really, really good."},{"time":604368,"text":"They switch really fast, very swiftly. They pay a very small cost."}]},{"cues":[{"time":608851,"text":"Now I'd like you to remember that result, and put it"},{"time":611509,"text":"in the context of another group of technology users,"},{"time":615241,"text":"a group which is actually much revered by society,"},{"time":617651,"text":"which are people that engage in multimedia-tasking."},{"time":622190,"text":"What is multimedia-tasking? It's the fact that most of us,"},{"time":625835,"text":"most of our children, are engaged with listening to music"},{"time":629116,"text":"at the same time as they're doing search on the web"},{"time":631863,"text":"at the same time as they're chatting on Facebook with their friends."},{"time":635220,"text":"That's a multimedia-tasker."},{"time":637556,"text":"There was a first study done by colleagues at Stanford"},{"time":641116,"text":"and that we replicated that showed that"},{"time":643669,"text":"those people that identify as being high multimedia-taskers"},{"time":648316,"text":"are absolutely abysmal at multitasking."},{"time":652163,"text":"When we measure them in the lab, they're really bad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":654900,"text":"Right? So these kinds of results really"},{"time":657606,"text":"makes two main points."},{"time":660092,"text":"The first one is that not all media are created equal."},{"time":663284,"text":"You can't compare the effect of multimedia-tasking"},{"time":668196,"text":"and the effect of playing action games. They have"},{"time":669842,"text":"totally different effects on different aspects of cognition,"},{"time":673234,"text":"perception and attention."},{"time":676348,"text":"Even within video games, I'm telling you right now"},{"time":679188,"text":"about these action-packed video games."},{"time":680941,"text":"Different video games have a different effect on your brains."},{"time":684275,"text":"So we actually need to step into the lab and really measure"},{"time":686957,"text":"what is the effect of each video game."}]},{"cues":[{"time":689468,"text":"The other lesson is that general wisdom carries no weight."},{"time":693755,"text":"I showed that to you already, like we looked at the fact that"},{"time":696811,"text":"despite a lot of screen time, those action gamers"},{"time":699259,"text":"have a lot of very good vision, etc."},{"time":703267,"text":"Here, what was really striking is that these undergraduates"},{"time":706585,"text":"that actually report engaging in a lot of high"},{"time":709826,"text":"multimedia-tasking are convinced they aced the test."},{"time":714803,"text":"So you show them their data, you show them they are bad"},{"time":717093,"text":"and they're like, \"Not possible.\" You know, they have"},{"time":719779,"text":"this sort of gut feeling that, really, they are doing really, really good."},{"time":723635,"text":"That's another argument for why we need to step into the lab"},{"time":726580,"text":"and really measure the impact of technology on the brain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":730172,"text":"Now in a sense, when we think about the effect"},{"time":734755,"text":"of video games on the brain, it's very similar"},{"time":737235,"text":"to the effect of wine on the health."},{"time":741099,"text":"There are some very poor uses of wine. There are some"},{"time":744139,"text":"very poor uses of video games. But when consumed"},{"time":748355,"text":"in reasonable doses, and at the right age,"},{"time":751836,"text":"wine can be very good for health. There are actually"},{"time":755107,"text":"specific molecules that have been identified"},{"time":758371,"text":"in red wine as leading to greater life expectancy."},{"time":764203,"text":"So it's the same way, like those action video games"},{"time":767475,"text":"have a number of ingredients that are actually really"},{"time":769137,"text":"powerful for brain plasticity, learning, attention,"},{"time":773107,"text":"vision, etc., and so we need and we're working on"},{"time":776712,"text":"understanding what are those active ingredients so that"},{"time":779467,"text":"we can really then leverage them to deliver better games,"},{"time":783357,"text":"either for education or for rehabilitation of patients."}]},{"cues":[{"time":787600,"text":"Now because we are interested in having an impact"},{"time":791379,"text":"for education or rehabilitation of patients, we are actually"},{"time":793867,"text":"not that interested in how those of you that choose"},{"time":797283,"text":"to play video games for many hours on end perform."},{"time":801155,"text":"I'm much more interested in taking any of you"},{"time":804980,"text":"and showing that by forcing you to play an action game,"},{"time":808760,"text":"I can actually change your vision for the better,"},{"time":811623,"text":"whether you want to play that action game or not, right?"},{"time":813954,"text":"That's the point of rehabilitation or education."},{"time":816370,"text":"Most of the kids don't go to school saying,"},{"time":818296,"text":"\"Great, two hours of math!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":821036,"text":"So that's really the crux of the research, and to do that,"},{"time":825475,"text":"we need to go one more step."},{"time":827939,"text":"And one more step is to do training studies."},{"time":830963,"text":"So let me illustrate that step with"},{"time":834363,"text":"a task which is called mental rotation."},{"time":837931,"text":"Mental rotation is a task where I'm going to ask you,"},{"time":842106,"text":"and again you're going to do the task,"},{"time":843991,"text":"to look at this shape. Study it, it's a target shape,"},{"time":847676,"text":"and I'm going to present to you four different shapes."},{"time":850930,"text":"One of these four different shapes is actually a rotated"},{"time":853770,"text":"version of this shape. I want you to tell me which one:"},{"time":858074,"text":"the first one, second one, third one or fourth one?"},{"time":862915,"text":"Okay, I'll help you. Fourth one."},{"time":865332,"text":"One more. Get those brains working. Come on."},{"time":869862,"text":"That's our target shape."},{"time":874836,"text":"Third. Good! This is hard, right?"},{"time":878539,"text":"Like, the reason that I asked you to do that is because"},{"time":880026,"text":"you really feel your brain cringing, right?"},{"time":882760,"text":"It doesn't really feel like playing mindless action video games."}]},{"cues":[{"time":886192,"text":"Well, what we do in these training studies is, people"},{"time":888897,"text":"come to the lab, they do tasks like this one,"},{"time":891506,"text":"we then force them to play 10 hours of action games."},{"time":895836,"text":"They don't play 10 hours of action games in a row."},{"time":898582,"text":"They do distributed practice, so little shots of 40 minutes"},{"time":901692,"text":"several days over a period of two weeks."},{"time":905993,"text":"Then, once they are done with the training, they come back"},{"time":907789,"text":"a few days later and they are tested again on a similar type"},{"time":911762,"text":"of mental rotation task. So this is work from a colleague"},{"time":915378,"text":"in Toronto. What they showed is that, initially,"},{"time":917913,"text":"you know, subjects perform where they are expected"},{"time":920111,"text":"to perform given their age. After two weeks of training"},{"time":925321,"text":"on action video games, they actually perform better,"},{"time":929177,"text":"and the improvement is still there five months after"},{"time":934533,"text":"having done the training. That's really, really important."},{"time":937401,"text":"Why? Because I told you we want to use these games"},{"time":939881,"text":"for education or for rehabilitation. We need to have effects"},{"time":943081,"text":"that are going to be long-lasting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":946017,"text":"Now, at this point, a number of you are probably wondering"},{"time":948870,"text":"well, what are you waiting for, to put on the market"},{"time":952503,"text":"a game that would be good for the attention"},{"time":955055,"text":"of my grandmother and that she would actually enjoy,"},{"time":958575,"text":"or a game that would be great to rehabilitate the vision"},{"time":961158,"text":"of my grandson who has amblyopia, for example?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":964967,"text":"Well, we're working on it, but here is a challenge."},{"time":969447,"text":"There are brain scientists like me that are beginning"},{"time":971358,"text":"to understand what are the good ingredients in games"},{"time":974615,"text":"to promote positive effects, and that's what I'm going"},{"time":977720,"text":"to call the broccoli side of the equation."},{"time":981294,"text":"There is an entertainment software industry"},{"time":985030,"text":"which is extremely deft at coming up with"},{"time":988502,"text":"appealing products that you can't resist."},{"time":992646,"text":"That's the chocolate side of the equation."},{"time":996174,"text":"The issue is we need to put the two together,"},{"time":999198,"text":"and it's a little bit like with food."},{"time":1001454,"text":"Who really wants to eat chocolate-covered broccoli?"},{"time":1005095,"text":"None of you. (Laughter) And you probably have had"},{"time":1007354,"text":"that feeling, right, picking up an education game"},{"time":1009686,"text":"and sort of feeling, hmm, you know, it's not really fun,"},{"time":1013078,"text":"it's not really engaging. So what we need"},{"time":1015495,"text":"is really a new brand of chocolate, a brand of chocolate"},{"time":1018846,"text":"that is irresistible, that you really want to play,"},{"time":1022857,"text":"but that has all the ingredients, the good ingredients"},{"time":1025842,"text":"that are extracted from the broccoli that you can't recognize"},{"time":1029070,"text":"but are still working on your brains. And we're working on it,"},{"time":1031909,"text":"but it takes brain scientists to come and to get together,"},{"time":1036385,"text":"people that work in the entertainment software industry,"},{"time":1039348,"text":"and publishers, so these are not people that usually"},{"time":1042086,"text":"meet every day, but it's actually doable,"},{"time":1044423,"text":"and we are on the right track."},{"time":1047070,"text":"I'd like to leave you with that thought,"},{"time":1048852,"text":"and thank you for your attention. (Applause)"},{"time":1052219,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}